name: UConstantQNRT
doc:
UConstantQNRT

UConstantQNRT calculates the temporal evolution of constant q transform for a given
sound. ConstantQ is available for individual channels or the overall sound asset.

Settings: The settings for the audio analyzer.

methods.name: GetChannelConstantQAtTime
methods.doc: Get a specific channel cqt of the analyzed sound at a given time.

methods.name: GetNormalizedChannelConstantQAtTime
methods.doc: Get a specific channel cqt of the analyzed sound at a given time.
